ISLAMABAD, Apr 19 (APP): The Senate on Wednesday offered Fateha for the departed soul of former Minister for Religious Affairs and Interfaith Harmony Mufti Abdul Shakoor, who lost his life in a tragic traffic accident in Islamabad.
Senator Haji Hidayatullah led Fateha on the request of Senate Chairman Muhammad Sadiq Sanjrani.
